## ğŸ”§ Features

* ğŸ“„ PDF Upload & FAISS Vector Indexing
* ğŸ’¬ Chat interface for querying PDF contents
* ğŸ§  LLM-powered answer generation using LangChain & HuggingFace
* ğŸ¨ Beautiful animated UI with background gradients
* ğŸ“¥ Auto-scroll, typing animation, and WhatsApp-style chat bubbles

